Make a bookmarklet out of this script (How to make a bookmarklet is on SecurlyKiller 106+): 
javascript:(function () {var a = document.createElement('script');a.src = 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/FogNetwork/Ingot/ingot.min.js';document.body.appendChild(a);}())
Go to chrome.google.com/webstorex
Open the bookmarklet you just made.
Select the extensions you want disabled.
